{"title":"Arritmias","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Arritmias-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Arritmias","guid":"K71LmWA6wEdOr2PH0-mx_w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación:","guid":"nrRde3jwMjZKr1cF-HPjCg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Bradiarritmias","guid":"xSRsJxZ9CF6crNNDi0mfQA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Definición: FC < 60 lpm.","guid":"7J3RiA1nbKqDVNQhhKNzLw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Tipos:","guid":"egQYkropW2YThaq9x8RFyg","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Disfunción del nodo sinusal","guid":"YxD6-LwNSNpw_i1ckhEYRA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Bloqueo AV","guid":"y5Pj19-gi-ceSGc9Qt0kVQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"2. Taquiarritmias","guid":"gWzWD1NY3lujScbwqc11iA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Definición: FC > 100 lpm.","guid":"BY8AlN55T2VpdeNSiqBQIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"3. Taquiarritmias\\Nsupraventriculares","guid":"XvjmI0vASUz91zkzUUAT8g","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Definición: Origina en nodo SA, miocardio auricular o nodo AV\\N→ QRS regular.","guid":"Qlvp0s4NOu1IuHlDfAmABQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Tipos:","guid":"6o7VEkbGE2nEkmWZI7OtBQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Fibrilación auricular (FA)","guid":"F2TOVQWYWZJ_kAkFSjOsSA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Flutter auricular","guid":"M91Z2nLQ-f7LcwyyT94zfQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"Taquicardia supraventricular paroxística (TSVP)","guid":"icejYrNbu8M_MJvypL2lbA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"4. Taquiarritmias\\Nventriculares","guid":"cIIVY4I8A7RXn-CNRV0thQ","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Definición: Origina por debajo del nodo AV → QRS ancho.","guid":"3Ld5PVZBRkUKROtOt6Lu5Q","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Tipos:","guid":"Pim00b7k0Urq2lnyiopNUw","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Taquicardia ventricular (TV)","guid":"ndkds2iAggmq5rCi3Gok6w","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Fibrilación ventricular (FV)","guid":"QiKGqYFLwv3DR_5LyEuUXQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Bradiarritmias","guid":"Kn06NyOpN_axgHY90aPdaQ","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"1. Origen auricular:","guid":"yIPVjc6GGjcBs9y4VtIioA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Arritmia sinusal\\Nrespiratoria","guid":"icctH-64F2W7r4XLaTT_1Q","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Fisiológica, común en jóvenes","guid":"-RB8EMUn8YLX1v3ZcuWK2w","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• Cambios menores en el intervalo R-R durante respiración\\N→ ↓ durante inspiración, ↑ durante espiración","guid":"g6j8emHL3OgBNweUXr1mzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Bradicardia\\Nsinusal","guid":"BClKByZ6kbyGTk4bKHarfA","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Fisiológica, especialmente en deportistas","guid":"4ne1nlzOADdkdFxr1PVHTw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Disfunción del nodo sinusal (ver síndrome del nodo enfermo)","guid":"-Wk7EzlEVOrLOi9S1mFGRg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• Fármacos: β-bloqueadores, bloqueadores de canales de Ca","guid":"smpNvwp97K_rnu5SJG_oiQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"• FC < 60 lpm","guid":"rMApDMJQ-gcxPBM6OESesQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"• Onda P normal antes de cada complejo QRS","guid":"2e01oe2fXepXD0deIWJZ2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"21","text":"Pausa o\\Nparo sinusal","guid":"n2dgO0qHhnL2STC-QEcisQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Puede ocurrir en individuos sanos","guid":"8SC6lZz_nUgMZQ0B2GFCUg","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• Enfermedad cardiovascular subyacente\\N(ver síndrome del nodo enfermo)","guid":"KSK0uyRewYMXPy4jKYwe1g","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"• Ausencia transitoria (pausa) o completa (paro) de la onda P","guid":"GyNNinRTfyC3ZPcgVB2jZA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"• A menudo con ritmo de escape (origen variable)","guid":"Je_iifjp3YuYJievJRJQ9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"21","text":"Síndrome\\Ntaquicardia-bradicardia","guid":"daT163OTq1u3Xz9rObJbYA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Alteración en la generación y conducción del impulso supraventricular","guid":"p2pmIEsEFKt8JRVYuiCEcQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• Ver síndrome del nodo enfermo para detalles","guid":"id_mujjGXNEpy88t2T-Gkg","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"• Alternancia de taquiarritmias y bradiarritmias","guid":"ZJ_nASb8DqnoOXzxzAYIHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"20","text":"2. Origen en nodo AV:","guid":"Q7_N63R82_Jsn5GkLT8T1A","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Bloqueo auriculoventricular\\N(AV)","guid":"L9Lf5jAzkVpmjZs4DDO4rw","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Bloqueo de\\Nprimer grado","guid":"GpgsgcqgrCWknYVjAw6lOg","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Respuesta fisiológica","guid":"g07G-Zllkjfurbh_Ky7Oww","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• ↑ Tono vagal","guid":"OxkFKeeT1qITjhuqfiuE-g","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Fármacos: β-bloqueadores, bloqueadores de canales de Ca","guid":"KTC0p8oNiJDByMftJBDZkQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"• Intervalo PR > 200 ms","guid":"qU1RPOTGj0PXujFeRMtV-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"Bloqueo de\\Nsegundo grado","guid":"HpJ9-4_dyumv8OQaiuuoHQ","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Fármacos: digoxina, β-bloqueadores, bloqueadores de canales de Ca","guid":"bUFJx6CUjrWuPM-uOipgBA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• ↑ Tono vagal","guid":"ZUakh9E4MUrHyHKc9Ah5XQ","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Enfermedad de conducción sinoauricular","guid":"tjPgeN77ZVNz8m3JWvMpKg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"• Infarto coronario derecho","guid":"MLfevmDyBKYzvEG-HSQz6w","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"• Mobitz tipo I/Wenckebach: alargamiento progresivo del\\Nintervalo PR hasta que se omite un latido","guid":"y6m7KrE5-r0cs4NshNyILQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"47","text":"• Mobitz tipo II: latidos\\Nomitidos de forma irregular","guid":"GzWrvBMOGWcOn7_oc7PWbw","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"41","text":"Bloqueo de\\Ntercer grado","guid":"fY69cmwZ4M-p9tgjHOFWgA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Bloqueo completo: sin comunicación entre aurículas y ventrículos","guid":"xCHqPBpMt-IH2TbIgws2bQ","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• Disociación AV: no hay relación entre ondas P y complejos QRS","guid":"nBJJEdN77x5nP2cuESYQog","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Taquiarritmias Supraventriculares","guid":"2OJAVpWvuOeJ5h4oEz2R6w","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"1. Extrasístoles\\Nsupraventriculares","guid":"7yyiR7Yet_rKTfmA9O6qXg","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Respuesta fisiológica, desequilibrio electrolítico, enfermedad cardiovascular","guid":"Ui347bWIVTxlNX4qc5lWSA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Anomalías en la onda P o ausencia de onda P","guid":"Gt2zzuR0Y-yCPse5LMtdLw","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"2. Taquicardia\\Nsinusal","guid":"lPqNshfvDuU2W64BoPVlZQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Activación simpática o ↓ tono vagal en nodo SA","guid":"G27PbmYUHYo5s9FuRRxrSA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• Comienzo gradual, ritmo regular","guid":"Wc1QTp4Qmdt19h8tT3AIgA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"• FC máx: 180 lpm, onda P normal, QRS estrecho","guid":"l6Vx78xto9uE7k27apHB6g","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"57","text":"3. Flutter\\Nauricular","guid":"s-iepcA5A3fP_zIafLHWbQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Ritmo macroreentrante en las aurículas","guid":"iENf3nGrf-QvoLm47dTP2A","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Ritmo regular, FC auricular 250-350, FC ventricular < 200","guid":"aG8oiRpEC3xBVSSwe0kPPA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"• Onda P en \"dientes de sierra\" (II, III, aVF), QRS estrecho","guid":"vz3jqJMcMzUV50lHKpOQTg","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"57","text":"4. Fibrilación\\Nauricular","guid":"LdP7ydsNWUbzZ3ya0OFAFg","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Múltiples mecanismos","guid":"fWf6TZpBvbtZPMie4zYXoQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Ritmo irregularmente irregular, FC auricular 350-450, ventricular < 200","guid":"c_Gb3L_YPlfAOW_dwDm8Ng","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"• Ondas P indiscernibles, QRS estrecho","guid":"m3OyzddPV3O5jr9JI_7W6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"57","text":"5. Taquicardia auricular focal\\N(~5%)","guid":"Bu13z-tAwcoWM8fgJSXmEQ","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Descarga de un foco ectópico en la aurícula","guid":"q_EeitRrEVWs9QtVljgX1Q","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Comienzo abrupto, ritmo regular","guid":"FaAAgSuGLQLGhNkjMJZE7A","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• FC: 150-250, onda P morfología variable, QRS estrecho","guid":"Gzl6CVGtrZ7kH1rqZ4pchA","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"57","text":"6. Taquicardia auricular multifocal\\N(TAM)","guid":"kHAKr-bdyl3uFcY1pcOdXQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Múltiples focos ectópicos auriculares","guid":"e4P0YARIAOvisQvbtKLnrg","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"• Asociada a EPOC, embolismo pulmonar, ICC, teofilina","guid":"nPHOwZdEs2UPbM2b6glCqA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"• Ritmo irregularmente irregular, FC: 150-250","guid":"Dy8rJOI8JZyaKXJby6cqkA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"• Ondas P discernibles con ≥ 3 morfologías diferentes, QRS estrecho","guid":"8GJuOmzLKhbIQtaoo3CqTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"57","text":"7. Taquicardia por reentrada AV\\N(AVRT)","guid":"2iV-rGHS_Qxk45BbBV4wVQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Vía accesoria entre aurículas y ventrículos","guid":"IYhwZdlWOz8pHKOKZt_Spw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Comienzo abrupto, ritmo regular, FC: 150-250","guid":"8oFZI7AMbO40aSPFr5oECQ","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"• Onda P invertida post-QRS, RP < PR, QRS estrecho (ortodrómica)\\No ancho con ondas delta (antidrómica)","guid":"IM2C7a4iLgEZVl1qHwDBfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"57","text":"8. Taquicardia por reentrada en nodo AV\\N(AVNRT)","guid":"t5RNDVhjHFHBFKdcw4naBQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• Nodo AV con dos vías eléctricas","guid":"zuVvzMuiRSCJTsgiUdze6w","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"• Ritmo regular, FC: 150-250","guid":"fGZro70iKaDwj6okk_5Kmw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"• Onda P oculta en QRS o post-QRS, QRS estrecho, RP < PR","guid":"UtlhY1KtiBiDjmdzaZlJEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"57","text":"9. Taquicardia por foco nodal\\N(de la unión)","guid":"6KKXKgrSrohJLMitryYdPg","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• Nodo AV como marcapasos","guid":"RGBZ7RwTAjlcHgDsrDqLgQ","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"• Toxicidad digitálica, miocarditis, IAM","guid":"YIYrs3KSiiBLWoN-dZEdVQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"• Ritmo regular, FC: 100-130","guid":"G30EAXy3tiMJsjVn17W52Q","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"• Onda P invertida antes, durante o después del QRS, QRS estrecho","guid":"RC0GqGoGrK9D73YqMsLYQg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Taquiarritmias Ventriculares","guid":"muh2RE48cFoeTG6np7Jc9w","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"1. Extrasístoles\\Nventriculares","guid":"2wfYFs1pdVP8jHaJWBO5tA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Foco ectópico ventricular (hipoxia, hipertiroidismo, alteraciones electrolíticas)","guid":"z3jC7w3bBcQm2CrMc3BRYQ","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• QRS ancho prematuro sin onda P, pausa compensatoria","guid":"r2UHZCLtO_owYmU7CEaxCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"2. Taquicardia\\Nventricular (TV)","guid":"gE0vtHneloazS7kV2CunzQ","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• CAD, IAM, enfermedades cardíacas estructurales","guid":"iRAaeMQbZXs-jnnJ7U0-Fg","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"• Ritmo regular, rápido","guid":"YAG8_9Hfvg1QgTLBss_axg","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"• QRS ancho (≥ 3 extrasístoles ventriculares consecutivas), disociación AV","guid":"j47HOrMaiwrJVXRulbfngQ","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"99","text":"• TV monomórfica: morfología única","guid":"irsxxk9tL7Jr_mk8ZCX_cQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"99","text":"• TV polimórfica: múltiples morfologías de QRS","guid":"Kurn9X659bDLPcKTPc0p1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"95","text":"3. Torsades\\Nde pointes","guid":"IS6DROgyEGzg10vN7OTlqA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Sx QT largo, fármacos proarrítmicos, hipopotasemia","guid":"l8gsIp-AtDwBpTlFkZ18CQ","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• TV polimórfica con QRS que parece girar alrededor de la línea isoeléctrica","guid":"lONHPGYk80rAF3bwCCD58w","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"95","text":"4. Fibrilación\\Nventricular (FV)","guid":"1q8JP77gbA8JEcIdt918Qg","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• IAM, enfermedades cardíacas estructurales","guid":"qoDn5itVu8c7M6WPtL5PQA","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• Línea de base arrítmica, fibrilatoria, > 300 lpm","guid":"Bu2ZaI7TH8dKLz3fEg3Dlg","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• Ondulaciones erráticas, sin QRS discernibles","guid":"iJhOWOQJtziCMJgdh7EeBQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":111,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Arritmias-2024","id":"map_227","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Arritmias-2024"}